{% comment %} Bespoke content for the Luma Luxury Mattress product — layer diagram, comfort
   scale, feature cards, comparison table, testimonial, size guide, FAQ. Ported verbatim
   from luma-luxury.html. Rendered by sections/main-product.liquid via two parts: 'spec'
   (inside the buy panel) and 'body' (the "Inside the Luma" section onward). Note: Luma
   Luxury has EIGHT layers (A–H), unlike the seven-layer Classic/Premium. {% endcomment %}

{% case part %}

{% when 'spec' %}
    <div class="spec-mini">
        <div><b>Thickness</b>10"</div>
        <div><b>Comfort Scale</b>Medium Soft</div>
        <div><b>Best for</b>Side sleepers, hotel-like plush feel</div>
    </div>

{% when 'body' %}
    <section class="story section--dark">
        <blockquote>Obsessed with mattresses, <em>so you can be obsessed with sleep.</em></blockquote>
        <p>Every Luma Luxury fuses traditional craftsmanship with innovative foam technology — certified foams, precision quilting, and a layer stack we've refined year after year, backed by a 7-year warranty.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="inside">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;max-width:620px;margin-left:0;">
                <h2>Eight layers of engineered comfort</h2>
                <p>Tap a layer to see what it does. Luma Luxury adds Memorest Foam above the Pro Nexa layer — a plusher comfort zone above the same Hybrid Pocket Spring core, now a full 10 inches tall.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="layers-grid">
                <svg class="layer-svg" viewBox="0 0 520 474" role="img" aria-label="Cross-section of the Luma Luxury mattress showing eight layers">
                    <g id="slabA" class="slab" data-layer="A">
                        <path d="M30 44 Q30 22 66 22 L454 22 Q490 22 490 44 L490 58 L30 58 Z" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
